$mod+F3: Call a dmenu script to open PCManFM on specific directories
PrtScr: Screenshot
$mod+PrtScr: Screenshot focused window
$mod+Shift+PrtScr: Screenshot with selection

$mod+`: Show scratchpad windows
$mod+Shift+`: Move to scratchpad
$mod+[0-9]: Go to workspace [1-10]
$mod+Shift+[0-9]: Move container to workspace [1-10]
$mod+plus: Inner gaps +5
$mod+Shift+plus: Outer gaps +5
$mod+minus: Inner gaps -5
$mod+Shift+minus: Outer gaps -5

$mod+Shift+q: Kill focused container
$mod+w: Toggle tabbed layout
$mod+Shift+w: Change wallpaper
$mod+e: Toggle split
$mod+Shift+e: Exit i3
$mod+r: Ranger
$mod+Shift+r: Restart i3
$mod+t: Todo app on dmenu
$mod+Shift+t: Mark as done in todo app
$mod+Shift+i: Open ~/wallpapers folder in ranger
$mod+p: Picture in picture mode
$mod+Shift+p: Like PiP mode, but larger and sticky

$mod+a: Focus parent container
$mod+Shift+a: Set default gaps
$mod+s: Toggle stacked layout
$mod+Shift+s: Toggle sticky
$mod+d: Rofi
$mod+Shift+d: Dmenu
$mod+f: Toggle fullscreen
$mod+l: Lockscreen script
$mod+h: Split horizontal
$mod+Shift+[hjkl]: Resize
$mod+Return: Terminal(st)
$mod+Shift+Return: Floating terminal(st)

$mod+z: Tiny box terminal window
$mod+Shift+z: Resize current window to tiny box mode
$mod+Shift+c: Reload i3 config
$mod+v: Split vertical
$mod+b: Firefox
$mod+Shift+b: Firefox Private Window
$mod+m: Music script

$mod+Space: Change between floating and tiled windows
$mod+Shift+Space: Toggle floating
$mod+[Arrow Keys]: Shift focus to adjacent windows
